# Security headers for static assets served directly by the Cloudflare
# Workers assets binding (prerendered pages, /_astro/*, images), which bypass
# the worker. SSR responses get the same set from src/middleware.ts — keep
# both in sync. CSP frame-ancestors (not X-Frame-Options) lets the hosted
# Sanity Studio iframe site pages for draft preview while blocking every other
# origin. The Core-app Studio is sandboxed under *.sanity.studio nested inside
# the www.sanity.io dashboard shell, so both families are allowed (Sanity's
# documented set); localhost:3333 is local `sanity dev`.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors https://*.sanity.io https://*.sanity.studio http://localhost:3333
